urgery\", \"from\": 675, \"to\": 682}, {\"ngram\": \"her shoulder\", \"from\": 686, \"to\": 698}, {\"ngram\": \"thesurfingat the2024 Olympics\", \"from\": 730, \"to\": 759}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Surfing Games\", \"from\": 774, \"to\": 797}, {\"ngram\": \"March\", \"from\": 816, \"to\": 821}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Doing so may have been a logistical impossibility in any case, given the women's medals were only awarded in the early hours of Tuesday morning, almost 10,000 miles away from Paris, in Tahiti.\", \"from\": 824, \"to\": 1016, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 999, \"end\": 1004, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999989386197, \"rank\": 1.0613028611484894e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1009, \"end\": 1015, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999395459342579, \"rank\": 6.036118466434152e-05, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a logistical impossibility\", \"from\": 847, \"to\": 873}, {\"ngram\": \"any case\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 885}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's medals\", \"from\": 893, \"to\": 911}, {\"ngram\": \"the early hours\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 948}, {\"ngram\": \"Tuesday morning\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 967}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That, though, is unlikely to be an issue in LA and Brown, who spends much of her time in California, is desperate to be in action on two boards.\", \"from\": 1018, \"to\": 1162, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1107, \"end\": 1117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\", \"score\": 0.999558685066252, \"rank\": 0.0004329983803934512, \"text\": \"California\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an issue\", \"from\": 1050, \"to\": 1058}, {\"ngram\": \"LA\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1064}, {\"ngram\": \"Brown\", \"from\": 1069, \"to\": 1074}, {\"ngram\": \"her time\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1103}, {\"ngram\": \"action\", \"from\": 1141, \"to\": 1147}, {\"ngram\": \"two boards\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1161}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympics 2024 medal table and latest count today Olympics 2024: Every Team GB medal winner at the Paris Games so far \\\"I am a double Olympic medallist,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1164, \"to\": 1327, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympics 2024 medal table\", \"from\": 1164, \"to\": 1189}, {\"ngram\": \"latest count\", \"from\": 1194, \"to\": 1206}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympics\", \"from\": 1213, \"to\": 1221}, {\"ngram\": \"Every Team GB medal winner\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1254}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1273}, {\"ngram\": \"a double Olympic medallist\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1313}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's really cool and I am very happy.\", \"from\": 1328, \"to\": 1366, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When I go to LA, I am hoping to be a double Olympian there in surfing and skating.\", \"from\": 1367, \"to\": 1449, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1411, \"end\": 1419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999969718374, \"rank\": 3.027997675865679e-09, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"LA\", \"from\": 1380, \"to\": 1382}, {\"ngram\": \"surfing\", \"from\": 1429, \"to\": 1436}, {\"ngram\": \"skating\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1448}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every time I lose, I learn, and I learn a lot every day and I can bring that to LA.\\\"\", \"from\": 1450, \"to\": 1534, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1490, \"to\": 1495}, {\"ngram\": \"LA\", \"from\": 1530, \"to\": 1532}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are, however, other tasks for the teenager to tick off before then.\", \"from\": 1536, \"to\": 1609, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"other tasks\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1567}, {\"ngram\": \"the teenager\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1584}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have some school work to do,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 1611, \"to\": 1654, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some school work\", \"from\": 1619, \"to\": 1635}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I can get my driver's licence in America.\", \"from\": 1655, \"to\": 1697, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my driver's licence\", \"from\": 1666, \"to\": 1685}, {\"ngram\": \"America\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1696}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I miss surfing right now, so I am hoping to get into the water straight away.\", \"from\": 1698, \"to\": 1775, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 1751, \"to\": 1760}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I need to get a shoulder surgery, but hopefully that will not take too long.\\\"\", \"from\": 1776, \"to\": 1857, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a shoulder surgery\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1812}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brown's participation in the final had at one stage looked in doubt, with the youngster in obvious discomfort when leaving the course at the end of qualifying.\", \"from\": 1859, \"to\": 2018, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Brown's participation\", \"from\": 1859, \"to\": 1880}, {\"ngram\": \"one stage\", \"from\": 1901, \"to\": 1910}, {\"ngram\": \"doubt\", \"from\": 1921, \"to\": 1926}, {\"ngram\": \"the youngster\", \"from\": 1933, \"to\": 1946}, {\"ngram\": \"obvious discomfort\", \"from\": 1950, \"to\": 1968}, {\"ngram\": \"the course\", \"from\": 1982, \"to\": 1992}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1996, \"to\": 2003}, {\"ngram\": \"qualifying\", \"from\": 2007, \"to\": 2017}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Afterwards, her father, Stewart, revealed she had effectively dislocated her shoulder again.\", \"from\": 2019, \"to\": 2111, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2043, \"end\": 2050, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_of_Stuart\", \"score\": 0.5472892140079028, \"rank\": 0.7456780287699601, \"text\": \"Stewart\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_of_Stuart\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/House_of_Stuart\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her father\", \"from\": 2031, \"to\": 2041}, {\"ngram\": \"her shoulder\", \"from\": 2092, \"to\": 2104}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It came out and popped back in,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2113, \"to\": 2155, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She did not even tell [the medical staff] it came out, because she was afraid they would pull her out.\", \"from\": 2156, \"to\": 2259, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the medical staff\", \"from\": 2180, \"to\": 2197}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I ran down to her and she said, 'Daddy, it's come out'.\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2315, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Then, as we were getting up, she said, 'Oh, I think it's gone back in'.\\\"\", \"from\": 2316, \"to\": 2388, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Remarkably, Brown was the oldest member of a podium that was headed by 14-year-old Australian Arisa Trew, with 15-year-old Japanese Cocona Hiraki taking silver.\", \"from\": 2390, \"to\": 2550, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2473, \"end\": 2483, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.999696045947231, \"rank\": 0.00020266204467751786, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 2484, \"end\": 2489, \"title\": \"http://db